    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1.0 at all 5 operating points with maximum deviation of 15% from experimental data. The team accepted the validation evidence generated under build 2026-q1-build-7-rc2 as applicable to the released build 2026-q1-build-7 on the basis of engineering judgment that no solver-kernel changes were introduced between the RC and release tags. The UnitOfAssurance is therefore accepted at Medium assurance level for MRL 2.",
